Class Summary
BaseEventEntry<E extends BaseEventEntry<E>> Customizes the base entry to define an event entry.
BaseEventEntry.EventStatus Defines the base set of values for event status.
BaseEventEntry.Transparency Defines the base set of values for event transparency.
BaseEventEntry.Visibility Defines the base set of values for event visibility.

ContactEntry Deprecated. Please use ContactEntry instead.

Email GData schema extension describing an email address.
Email.Rel The email type.
EntryLink<E extends BaseEntry<?>> The EntryLink class defines the object model for a link entity that refers to a GData entry.
EventEntry Extension class for manipulating entries of the Event kind.
EventFeed The EventFeed class customizes the generic event feed class to define a feed of events.
ExtendedProperty GData schema extension describing an entity's auxiliary property.
ExtendedProperty.Realm Limits on where the extended property applies.
FeedLink<F extends BaseFeed<?,?>> The FeedLink class defines the object model for a link entity that refers to a GData feed.
GeoPt Deprecated. Use com.google.gdata.data.geo.impl package.
Im Describes an instant messaging address.
Im.Protocol Im protocol.
Im.Rel Im type.
Image GData schema extension describing an image.
Image.Rel Image type.
Labels A utility aggregating gdata common data entry labels
MessageEntry Extension class for manipulating entries of the Message kind.
MessageFeed The Message class customizes the generic BaseEntry class to define a feed of Message entries.
Money Describes money.
Organization Describes an organization (like Company).
Organization.Rel Organization type.
OrgName Name of organization.
OrgTitle Position in organization.
OriginalEvent GData schema extension describing a link to a recurring event.
PhoneNumber GData schema extension describing a phone number.
PhoneNumber.Rel The phone number type.
PostalAddress GData schema extension describing a postal address.
PostalAddress.Rel The postal address type.
Rating GData schema extension describing an object's rating.
Rating.Rel Rating type.
Recurrence GData schema extension describing an RFC 2445 recurrence rule.
RecurrenceException GData schema extension describing individual exceptions to a recurring event.
Reminder GData schema extension describing a reminder on an event.
When GData schema extension describing a period of time.
Where GData schema extension describing a place (not necessarily a specific geographical location).
Where.Rel Relation type.
Who GData schema extension describing a person.
Who.AttendeeStatus Status of event attendee.
Who.AttendeeType Type of event attendee.
